p begin="00:31.061" end="00:33.468" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="00:31.061" end="00:31.366">I</span> <span begin="00:31.366" end="00:31.399">say</span> <span begin="00:31.399" end="00:31.596">your</span> <span begin="00:31.596" end="00:32.060">name</span> <span begin="00:32.060" end="00:32.224">but</span> <span begin="00:32.224" end="00:32.460">you're</span> <span begin="00:32.460" end="00:32.639">not</span> <span begin="00:32.639" end="00:33.468">around</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我呼喊着你的名字 但你不在身旁</span></p><p begin="00:36.021" end="00:38.990" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="00:36.021" end="00:36.068">I</span> <span begin="00:36.068" end="00:36.359">need</span> <span begin="00:36.359" end="00:36.700">you</span> <span begin="00:36.700" end="00:36.860">I</span> <span begin="00:36.860" end="00:37.100">need</span> <span begin="00:37.100" end="00:37.420">you</span> <span begin="00:37.420" end="00:37.599">I</span> <span begin="00:37.599" end="00:37.810">need</span> <span begin="00:37.810" end="00:38.140">you</span> <span begin="00:38.140" end="00:38.370">right</span> <span begin="00:38.370" end="00:38.990">now</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="00:38.903" end="00:39.609"><span begin="00:38.903" end="00:39.431">(Right</span> <span begin="00:39.431" end="00:39.609">now)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">现在</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我想要你 我渴望着你 此刻我需要你</span></p><p begin="00:39.609" end="00:41.230" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="00:39.609" end="00:39.799">Yeah</span> <span begin="00:39.799" end="00:40.068">I</span> <span begin="00:40.068" end="00:40.279">need</span> <span begin="00:40.279" end="00:40.399">you</span> <span begin="00:40.399" end="00:40.730">right</span> <span begin="00:40.730" end="00:41.230">now</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="00:41.364" end="00:41.880"><span begin="00:41.364" end="00:41.640">(Right</span> <span begin="00:41.640" end="00:41.880">now)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">现在</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN"> 此刻我需要你</span></p><p begin="00:42.020" end="00:44.619" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="00:42.020" end="00:42.239">So</span> <span begin="00:42.239" end="00:42.468">don't</span> <span begin="00:42.468" end="00:42.679">let</span> <span begin="00:42.679" end="00:42.860">me</span> <span begin="00:42.860" end="00:43.060">don't</span> <span begin="00:43.060" end="00:43.290">let</span> <span begin="00:43.290" end="00:43.490">me</span> <span begin="00:43.490" end="00:43.780">don't</span> <span begin="00:43.780" end="00:44.039">let</span> <span begin="00:44.039" end="00:44.228">me</span> <span begin="00:44.228" end="00:44.619">down</span> <span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="00:44.536" end="00:45.508"><span begin="00:44.536" end="00:44.752">(Don‘t</span> <span begin="00:44.752" end="00:44.986">let</span> <span begin="00:44.986" end="00:45.123">me</span> <span begin="00:45.123" end="00:45.508">down)</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">所以别让我苦苦等待 不要让我失望</span></p><p begin="00:45.294" end="00:47.219" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="00:45.294" end="00:45.481">I</span> <span begin="00:45.481" end="00:45.593">think</span> <span begin="00:45.593" end="00:45.787">I'm</span> <span begin="00:45.787" end="00:46.156">losing</span> <span begin="00:46.156" end="00:46.273">my</span> <span begin="00:46.273" end="00:46.669">mind</span> <span begin="00:46.669" end="00:47.219">now</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我想我已失去理智</span></p><p begin="00:47.345" end="00:50.079" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="00:47.345" end="00:47.566">It's</span> <span begin="00:47.566" end="00:47.795">in</span> <span begin="00:47.795" end="00:47.985">my</span> <span begin="00:47.985" end="00:48.403">head</span> <span begin="00:48.869" end="00:49.145">darling</span> <span begin="00:49.145" end="00:49.534">I</span> <span begin="00:49.635" end="00:50.079">hope</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">脑海里满是你的身影 我希望</span></p><p begin="00:50.406" end="00:53.158" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="00:50.406" end="00:50.694">That</span> <span begin="00:50.694" end="00:50.915">you'll</span> <span begin="00:50.915" end="00:51.115">be</span> <span begin="00:51.115" end="00:51.515">here</span> <span begin="00:51.515" end="00:51.694">when</span> <span begin="00:51.694" end="00:51.875">I</span> <span begin="00:51.875" end="00:52.145">need</span> <span begin="00:52.145" end="00:52.374">you</span> <span begin="00:52.374" end="00:52.534">the</span> <span begin="00:52.534" end="00:53.158">most</span> <span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我最需要你的时候 你能在我身边</span></p><p begin="00:53.195" end="00:56.739" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="00:53.195" end="00:54.035">So</span> <span begin="00:54.035" end="00:54.254">don't</span> <span begin="00:54.254" end="00:54.486">let</span> <span begin="00:54.486" end="00:54.745">me</span> <span begin="00:54.745" end="00:54.985">don't</span> <span begin="00:54.985" end="00:55.214">let</span> <span begin="00:55.214" end="00:55.475">me</span> <span begin="00:55.475" end="00:55.705">don't</span> <span begin="00:55.705" end="00:55.966">let</span> <span begin="00:55.966" end="00:56.174">me</span> <span begin="00:56.174" end="00:56.739">down</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">所以别让我苦苦等待 不要让我失望</span></p><p begin="00:57.814" end="01:00.151" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="00:57.814" end="00:58.065">Don't</span> <span begin="00:58.065" end="00:58.305">let</span> <span begin="00:58.305" end="00:58.505">me</span> <span begin="00:58.505" end="01:00.151">down</span> <span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">不要让我失望</span></p><p begin="01:03.810" end="01:06.055" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L15"><span begin="01:03.810" end="01:04.094">Don't</span> <span begin="01:04.094" end="01:04.345">let</span> <s