span begin="01:59.261" end="01:59.405">on</span> <span begin="01:59.405" end="01:59.612">my</span> <span begin="01:59.612" end="02:00.545">side</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我还以为你会在我身边</span></p><p begin="02:00.885" end="02:03.832" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L27"><span begin="02:00.885" end="02:01.084">But</span> <span begin="02:01.084" end="02:01.296">now</span> <span begin="02:01.296" end="02:01.466">there's</span> <span begin="02:01.466" end="02:02.218">nobody</span> <span begin="02:02.218" end="02:02.362">by</span> <span begin="02:02.362" end="02:02.533">my</span> <span begin="02:02.533" end="02:03.832">side</span> <span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="02:04.454" end="02:06.923"><span begin="02:04.454" end="02:04.715">(I</span> <span begin="02:04.715" end="02:05.002">need</span> <span begin="02:05.002" end="02:05.186">you</span> <span begin="02:05.186" end="02:06.144">right</span> <span begin="02:06.144" end="02:06.923">now)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我现在需要你</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">而此刻 无人在我身旁</span></p><p begin="02:05.858" end="02:09.193" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L28"><span begin="02:05.858" end="02:06.098">I</span> <span begin="02:06.098" end="02:06.298">need</span> <span begin="02:06.298" end="02:06.640">you</span> <span begin="02:06.640" end="02:06.800">I</span> <span begin="02:06.800" end="02:07.018">need</span> <span begin="02:07.018" end="02:07.349">you</span> <span begin="02:07.349" end="02:07.520">I</span> <span begin="02:07.520" end="02:07.778">need</span> <span begin="02:07.778" end="02:08.029">you</span> <span begin="02:08.029" end="02:08.280">right</span> <span begin="02:08.280" end="02:09.193">now</span> <span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="02:08.944" end="02:09.484"><span begin="02:08.944" end="02:09.277">(Right</span> <span begin="02:09.277" end="02:09.484">now)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">现在</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我想要你 我渴望着你 此刻我需要你</span></p><p begin="02:09.618" end="02:11.673" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L29"><span begin="02:09.618" end="02:09.818">Yeah</span> <span begin="02:09.818" end="02:10.040">I</span> <span begin="02:10.040" end="02:10.218">need</span> <span begin="02:10.218" end="02:10.519">you</span> <span begin="02:10.519" end="02:10.698">right</span> <span begin="02:10.698" end="02:11.673">now</span> <span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="02:11.293" end="02:11.574"><span begin="02:11.293" end="02:11.528">(Right</span> <span begin="02:11.528" end="02:11.574">now)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">现在</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">此刻我需要你</span></p><p begin="02:11.818" end="02:14.823" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L30"><span begin="02:11.818" end="02:12.048">So</span> <span begin="02:12.048" end="02:12.338">don't</span> <span begin="02:12.338" end="02:12.578">let</span> <span begin="02:12.578" end="02:12.800">me</span> <span begin="02:12.800" end="02:13.008">don't</span> <span begin="02:13.008" end="02:13.258">let</span> <span begin="02:13.258" end="02:13.488">me</span> <span begin="02:13.488" end="02:13.738">don't</span> <span begin="02:13.738" end="02:13.989">let</span> <span begin="02:13.989" end="02:14.207">me</span> <span begin="02:14.207" end="02:14.823">down</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN"> 所以别让我苦苦等待 不要让我失望</span></p><p begin="02:15.349" end="02:17.103" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L31"><span begin="02:15.349" end="02:15.538">I</span> <span begin="02:15.538" end="02:15.738">think</span> <span begin="02:15.738" end="02:15.949">I'm</span> <span begin="02:15.949" end="02:16.138">losing</span> <span begin="02:16.138" end="02:16.360">my</span> <span begin="02:16.360" end="02:16.688">mind</span> <span begin="02:16.688" end="02:17.103">now</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN"> 我想我已失去理智</span></p><p begin="02:17.328" end="02:20.073" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L32"><span begin="02:17.328" end="02:17.549">It's</span> <span begin="02:17.549" end="02:17.808">in</span> <span begin="02:17.808" end="02:18.000">my</span> <span begin="02:18.000" end="02:18.622">head</span> <span begin="02:18.768" end="02:19.008">darling</span> <span begin="02:19.008" end="02:19.509">I</span> <span begin="02:19.509" end="02:20.073">hope</span> <span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">脑海里满是你的身影 我希望</span></p><p begin="02:20.269" end="02:23.124" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L33"><span begin="02:20.269" end="02:20.520">That</span> <span begin="02:20.520" end="02:20.808">you'll</span> <span begin="02:20.808" end="02:20.978">be</span> <span begin="02:20.978" end="02:21.314">here</span> <span begin="02:21.408" end="02:21.608">when</span> <span begin="02:21.608" end="02:21.840">I</span> <span begin="02:21.840" end="02:22.058">need</span> <span begin="02:22.058" end="02:22.338">you</span> <span begin="02:22.338" end="02:22.509">the</span> <span begin="02:22.509" end="02:23.124">most</span> <span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我最需要你的时候 你能在我身边</span></p><p begin="02:23.229" end="02:26.804" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L34"><span begin="02:23.229" end="02:23.960">So</span> <span begin="02:23.960" end="02:24.240">don't</span> <span begin="02:24.240" end="02:24.448">let</span> <span begin="02:24.448" end="02:24.738">me</span> <span begin="02:24.738" end="02:25.007">don't</span> <span begin="02:25.007" end="02:25.200">let</span> <span begin="02:25.200" end="02:25.509">me</span> <span begin="02:25.509" end="02:25.749">don't</span> <span begin="02:25.749" end="02:26.040">let</span> <span begin="02:26.040" end="02:26.240">me</span> <span begin="02:26.240" end="02:26.804">down</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">所以别让我苦苦等待 不要让我失望</span></p><p begin="02:27.749" end="02:30.404" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L35"><span begin="02:27.749" end="02:28.008">Don't</span> <span begin="02:28.008" end="02:28.280">let</span> <span begin="02:28.280" end="02:28.480">me</span> <span beg